      h1 A day in Active

      p Class consists of a short (10-15 minutes) lecture, a question presented via Top Hat,  peer instruction and discussion of responses, a whole class discussion, a summary of the correct response, repeat.
      p Recitations consist of students working in small groups on worksheets, followed by whole class discussions.

