      h1 A day in Flipped

      p On Monday, Wednesday, and Friday, students complete online lessons instead of attending lecture.
      p On Tuesdays and Thursdays, students attend recitation either in person or synchronously through the web.
      p Recitations are centered around active learning with students working on problems in groups.

