        p Let <em>f</em> be a polynomial function.  Assume you know that the rate of change of <em>f</em> is always increasing on the <em>[a,b]</em>.
        p What can you say about <em>f</em>?
        ol(type="a")
          li <em>f</em> must have an absolute maximum value on <em>[a,b]</em> but it is unknown whether it has an absolute minimum value.
